<h3>Shrink that Pet!</h3>
<p>You've likely noticed that your pet is growing in size as you gain additional
spell circles.&nbsp; Sometimes your pet is larger than you'd like it to
be.&nbsp; Now, thanks to Tiny Companion you can shrink your pet!</p>
<p>It's a good idea to shrink your pet as a matter of course.&nbsp; Smaller pets
are much less likely to interfere with bolts -- and don't get in the way as much
in groups.</p>

